	the heat of dying flames
	<br> <br>
	burn me
	<br> <br>
	burn us.
	<br> <br>
	The last flicker of our souls give way,
	<br> <br>
	a passion soot remains,
	<br> <br>
	we drift softly into an embrace
	<br> <br>
	only to burn one another
	<br> <br>
