	</h1>
	<h3 class="piece_header"> This Place </h3>		
	<p>
	This Place
	<br> <br>
	All your life,
	<br> <br>
	you wanted to be
	<br> <br>
	someplace else.
	<br> <br>
	Now you are there
	<br> <br>
	and you don’t know
	<br> <br>
	what to do
	<br> <br>
	with yourself.
	<br> <br>
	So you sit and stare
	<br> <br>
	into the bottom of
	<br> <br>
	a half-empty glass,
	<br> <br>
	in hopes to catch a glance
	<br> <br>
	of a life to live for.
	</p>
